---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import MissionCtaBand from '../components/MissionCtaBand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About JILBIT" description="The story and mission behind JILBIT: Jesus Is Lord, Believe It.">
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-[#000000] px-6 py-16 text-left md:py-24">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,rgba(201,146,42,0.14),transparent_55%)]" />
    <div class="content-shell relative">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#5cd667]">Our Story</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 max-w-4xl text-4xl leading-tight text-[#faf7f2] md:text-6xl">About JILBIT</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-base text-[#faf7f2]/70 md:text-lg">
        JILBIT began as a simple confession among believers who wanted one message to shape everything: Jesus is Lord.
        What started as local encouragement evolved into a ministry focused on outreach, discipleship, and gospel-centered action.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-[#f0ebe0] px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="content-shell">
      <article class="rounded-lg border border-[rgba(92,61,46,0.15)] bg-white p-8 shadow-sm md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl leading-tight text-[#2e1a0e] md:text-4xl">Why it matters</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#7a6658]">
          In a culture of noise and uncertainty, people need clear hope. We believe the message of Jesus brings identity, purpose,
          healing, and eternal direction.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <MissionCtaBand />
</BaseLayout>
